  <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;line-height:
      36pt;color:#244061' lang=3Den-US><span style=3D'font-family:微軟正黑體;font-size:
      16.0pt'>Cerbral salt wasting</span></li>
  <ul type=3Ddisc style=3D'direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
   margin-bottom:0in'>
   <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;line-height:
       36pt;color:#244061'><span style=3D'font-family:微軟正黑體;font-size:14.0pt;
       color:#366092'>定義</span></li>
   <ul type=3Dcircle style=3D'direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
    margin-bottom:0in'>
    <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;line-height:
        36pt;color:#131314'><span style=3D'font-family:微軟正黑體;font-size:10.5pt;
        color:#131314;background:white'>大腦鹽耗症候群 (Cerebral salt wasting, CSW) 是</span><span
        style=3D'font-family:微軟正黑體;font-size:10.5pt;color:#C00000;background:
        white'>低血鈉伴隨尿鈉升高和低血容</span><span style=3D'font-family:微軟正黑體;font-size:
        10.5pt;color:#131314;background:white'>的現象</span></li>
   </ul>
  </ul>
  <ul type=3Ddisc style=3D'direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
   margin-bottom:0in'>
   <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;line-height:
       36pt'><span style=3D'font-family:微軟正黑體;font-size:14.0pt;color:#366092'
       lang=3Dzh-TW>流行病學</span><span style=3D'font-family:微軟正黑體;font-size:14.0pt;
       color:#366092' lang=3Den-US>&amp;</span><span style=3D'font-family:微軟正黑體;
       font-size:14.0pt;color:#366092' lang=3Dzh-TW>機制</span></li>
   <ul type=3Dcircle style=3D'direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
    margin-bottom:0in'>
    <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;line-height:
        36pt'><span style=3D'font-family:微軟正黑體;font-size:11.0pt'>發生原因不明</span></li>
    <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;line-height:
        36pt'><span style=3D'font-family:微軟正黑體;font-size:11.0pt'>常見於</span><span
        style=3D'font-weight:bold;font-family:微軟正黑體;font-size:11.0pt;color:#C00000'>蛛網膜下腔出血患者</span><span
        style=3D'font-family:微軟正黑體;font-size:11.0pt'>以及</span><span
        style=3D'font-weight:bold;font-family:微軟正黑體;font-size:11.0pt;color:#ED7D31'>神外手術術後患</span><span
        style=3D'font-family:微軟正黑體;font-size:11.0pt'>者</span></li>
   </ul>
  </ul>
  <ul type=3Ddisc style=3D'direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
   margin-bottom:0in'>
   <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;line-height:
       36pt;color:#366092'><span style=3D'font-family:微軟正黑體;font-size:14.0pt'>症狀</span></li>
   <ul type=3Dcircle style=3D'direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
    margin-bottom:0in'>
    <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;line-height:
        36pt'><span style=3D'font-family:微軟正黑體;font-size:11.0pt' lang=3Dzh-TW>低血容量、低張性低血鈉症</span><span
        style=3D'font-family:微軟正黑體;font-size:11.0pt' lang=3Den-US>(hypovolemic,
        hypotonic hyponatremia)</span></li>
    <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;line-height:
        36pt'><span style=3D'font-family:微軟正黑體;font-size:11.0pt'>可能併發多尿</span></li>
    <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;line-height:
        36pt'><span style=3D'font-family:微軟正黑體;font-size:11.0pt' lang=3Dzh-TW>術後</span><span
        style=3D'font-weight:bold;font-family:微軟正黑體;font-size:11.0pt;color:#C00000'
        lang=3Den-US>10</span><span style=3D'font-weight:bold;font-family:微軟正黑體;
        font-size:11.0pt;color:#C00000' lang=3Dzh-TW>天左右</span><span
        style=3D'font-family:微軟正黑體;font-size:11.0pt' lang=3Dzh-TW>發生</span></li>
   </ul>
   <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;line-height:
       36pt;color:#366092'><span style=3D'font-family:微軟正黑體;font-size:14.0pt'>診斷</span></li>
   <ul type=3Dcircle style=3D'direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
    margin-bottom:0in'>
    <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;line-height:
        36pt'><span style=3D'font-family:微軟正黑體;font-size:11.0pt'>低血容</span></li>
    <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;line-height:
        36pt'><span style=3D'font-family:微軟正黑體;font-size:11.0pt'>同時具備以下特徵：</span></li>
    <ul type=3Ddisc style=3D'direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
     margin-bottom:0in'>
     <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;line-height:
         36pt'><span style=3D'font-family:微軟正黑體;font-size:11.0pt'>血</span><span
         style=3D'font-family:微軟正黑體;font-size:11.0pt;color:#C00000'>鈉</span><span
         style=3D'font-family:微軟正黑體;font-size:11.0pt'>濃度</span><span
         style=3D'font-family:微軟正黑體;font-size:11.0pt;color:#C00000'>低於135 mEq/L</span><span
         style=3D'font-family:微軟正黑體;font-size:11.0pt'>，伴隨</span><span
         style=3D'font-family:微軟正黑體;font-size:11.0pt;color:#ED7D31'>低血漿滲透壓</span><span
         style=3D'font-family:微軟正黑體;font-size:11.0pt'>。</span></li>
     <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;line-height:
         36pt'><span style=3D'font-family:微軟正黑體;font-size:11.0pt' lang=3Dzh-TW>尿液滲透壓高於</span><span
         style=3D'font-family:微軟正黑體;font-size:11.0pt;color:#C00000' lang=3Dzh-TW>
         100 mosmol/kg</span><span style=3D'font-family:微軟正黑體;font-size:11.0pt'
         lang=3Den-US> (</span><span style=3D'font-family:微軟正黑體;font-size:11.0pt'
         lang=3Dzh-TW>常見高於 300 mosmol/kg）。</span></li>
    </ul>
    <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;line-height:
        36pt'><span style=3D'font-family:微軟正黑體;font-size:11.0pt;color:#ED7D31'>尿鈉</span><span
        style=3D'font-family:微軟正黑體;font-size:11.0pt'>濃度通常高於</span><span
        style=3D'font-family:微軟正黑體;font-size:11.0pt;color:#ED7D31'>40mEq/L</span><span
        style=3D'font-family:微軟正黑體;font-size:11.0pt'>。</span></li>
    <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;line-height:
        36pt'><span style=3D'font-family:微軟正黑體;font-size:11.0pt' lang=3Dzh-TW>CSW
        的診斷可能還需要觀察補充輸液後是否會導致尿液稀釋以</span><span style=3D'font-family:微軟正黑體;
        font-size:11.0pt' lang=3Den-US>rule out SI</span><span style=3D'font-family:
        微軟正黑體;font-size:11.0pt' lang=3Dzh-TW>ADH</span><span style=3D'font-family:
        微軟正黑體;font-size:11.0pt' lang=3Den-US>(</span><span style=3D'font-family:
        微軟正黑體;font-size:11.0pt' lang=3Dzh-TW>但不是絕對</span><span style=3D'font-family:
        微軟正黑體;font-size:11.0pt' lang=3Den-US>可以rule out</span><span
        style=3D'font-family:微軟正黑體;font-size:11.0pt' lang=3Dzh-TW>，目前仍有爭議</span><span
        style=3D'font-family:微軟正黑體;font-size:11.0pt' lang=3Den-US>)</span></li>
   </ul>
  </ul>
  <ul type=3Ddisc style=3D'direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
   margin-bottom:0in'>
   <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;line-height:
       36pt'><span style=3D'font-family:微軟正黑體;font-size:14.0pt;color:#366092'>治療</span></li>
   <ul type=3Dcircle style=3D'direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
    margin-bottom:0in'>
    <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;line-height:
        36pt'><span style=3D'font-family:微軟正黑體;font-size:11.0pt' lang=3Dzh-TW>近期開過刀或</span><span
        style=3D'font-family:微軟正黑體;font-size:11.0pt' lang=3Den-US>SAH:</span></li>
    <ul type=3Ddisc style=3D'direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
     margin-bottom:0in'>
     <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;line-height:
         36pt'><span style=3D'font-family:微軟正黑體;font-size:11.0pt' lang=3Dzh-TW>用</span><span
         style=3D'font-family:微軟正黑體;font-size:11.0pt;color:#70AD47' lang=3Den-US>3%
         Normal Saline</span><span style=3D'font-family:微軟正黑體;font-size:11.0pt'
         lang=3Dzh-TW>迅速增加血鈉</span></li>
    </ul>
    <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;line-height:
        36pt'><span style=3D'font-family:微軟正黑體;font-size:11.0pt' lang=3Dzh-TW>如果需要同時</span><span
        style=3D'font-family:微軟正黑體;font-size:11.0pt;color:#C00000' lang=3Dzh-TW>診斷加治療</span><span
        style=3D'font-family:微軟正黑體;font-size:11.0pt' lang=3Dzh-TW>可以試著用</span><span
        style=3D'font-family:微軟正黑體;font-size:11.0pt;color:#70AD47' lang=3Den-US>isotonic
        saline</span><span style=3D'font-family:微軟正黑體;font-size:11.0pt'
        lang=3Dzh-TW>。理論上是可以抑制</span><span style=3D'font-family:微軟正黑體;font-size:
        11.0pt' lang=3Den-US>ADH</span><span style=3D'font-family:微軟正黑體;font-size:
        11.0pt' lang=3Dzh-TW>釋放進而排出多餘的水，如果同時有</span><span style=3D'font-family:
        微軟正黑體;font-size:11.0pt' lang=3Den-US>SIADH</span><span style=3D'font-family:
        微軟正黑體;font-size:11.0pt' lang=3Dzh-TW>的病患通常可以讓尿液濃度由太高恢復正常；反之如果單純為</span><span
        style=3D'font-family:微軟正黑體;font-size:11.0pt' lang=3Den-US>CSW</span><span
        style=3D'font-family:微軟正黑體;font-size:11.0pt' lang=3Dzh-TW>患者則可能產生過度稀釋的尿液。</span></li>
    <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;line-height:
        36pt'><span style=3D'font-family:微軟正黑體;font-size:11.0pt'>給予口服</span><span
        style=3D'font-family:微軟正黑體;font-size:11.0pt;color:#70AD47'>鹽片</span><span
        style=3D'font-family:微軟正黑體;font-size:11.0pt'>緩解症狀</span></li>
    <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;line-height:
        36pt'><span style=3D'font-family:微軟正黑體;font-size:11.0pt;color:#70AD47'
        lang=3Den-US>fludrocortisone</span><span style=3D'font-family:微軟正黑體;
        font-size:11.0pt' lang=3Dzh-TW>亦有緩解功效</span></li>
    <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;line-height:
        36pt'><span style=3D'font-family:微軟正黑體;font-size:11.0pt' lang=3Dzh-TW>限水無效</span><span
        style=3D'font-family:微軟正黑體;font-size:11.0pt' lang=3Den-US>!(</span><span
        style=3D'font-family:微軟正黑體;font-size:11.0pt' lang=3Dzh-TW>但同樣可以診斷用，如果病人是</span><span
        style=3D'font-family:微軟正黑體;font-size:11.0pt' lang=3Den-US>SIADH</span><span
        style=3D'font-family:微軟正黑體;font-size:11.0pt' lang=3Dzh-TW>可兼治療</span><span
        style=3D'font-family:微軟正黑體;font-size:11.0pt' lang=3Den-US>)</span></li>
   </ul>
  </ul>
 </ul>
 <p style=3D'margin:0in;margin-left:.75in;font-family:微軟正黑體;font-size:14.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>
 <ul type=3Ddisc style=3D'direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
  margin-bottom:0in'>
  <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;color:#244061'
      lang=3Den-US><span style=3D'font-family:微軟正黑體;font-size:16.0pt'>SIADH</span></li>
  <ul type=3Ddisc style=3D'direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
   margin-bottom:0in'>
   <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;color:#366092'><span
       style=3D'font-family:微軟正黑體;font-size:14.0pt'>定義</span></li>
   <ul type=3Dcircle style=3D'direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
    margin-bottom:0in'>
    <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
        style=3D'font-family:微軟正黑體;font-size:11.0pt'>SIADH 是導致</span><span
        style=3D'font-weight:bold;font-family:微軟正黑體;font-size:11.0pt;color:#C00000'>等容積低滲透壓之低血鈉症</span><span
        style=3D'font-family:微軟正黑體;font-size:11.0pt'>（euvolemic hypotonic
        hyponatremia）最常見的原因。它是一種內分泌疾病，特徵為抗利尿激素（ADH）分泌過多或作用異常，導致腎臟過度保留水分，從而稀釋血液中的鈉濃度。</span></li>
   </ul>
   <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;color:#366092'><span
       style=3D'font-family:微軟正黑體;font-size:14.0pt'>機制</span></li>
   <ul type=3Dcircle style=3D'direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
    margin-bottom:0in'>
    <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
        style=3D'font-weight:bold;font-family:微軟正黑體;font-size:11.0pt;color:#ED7D31'>腦垂體分泌過多</span><span
        style=3D'font-family:微軟正黑體;font-size:11.0pt'>：例如由感染、藥物（像是抗精神病藥物或抗癲癇藥）引發。</span></li>
    <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
        style=3D'font-weight:bold;font-family:微軟正黑體;font-size:11.0pt;color:#ED7D31'
        lang=3Dzh-TW>異位分泌</span><span style=3D'font-weight:bold;font-family:微軟正黑體;
        font-size:11.0pt;color:#ED7D31' lang=3Den-US>(Ectopic ADH)</span><span
        style=3D'font-family:微軟正黑體;font-size:11.0pt' lang=3Dzh-TW>：例如</span><span
        style=3D'font-family:微軟正黑體;font-size:11.0pt;color:#C00000' lang=3Dzh-TW>小細胞肺癌</span><span
        style=3D'font-family:微軟正黑體;font-size:11.0pt' lang=3Dzh-TW>等惡性腫瘤異位產生 ADH。</span></li>
    <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
        style=3D'font-weight:bold;font-family:微軟正黑體;font-size:11.0pt;color:#ED7D31'
        lang=3Dzh-TW>腎臟 ADH 受體異常激活</span><span style=3D'font-family:微軟正黑體;
        font-size:11.0pt' lang=3Dzh-TW>：如</span><span style=3D'font-family:微軟正黑體;
        font-size:11.0pt' lang=3Den-US>X-linked recessive</span><span
        style=3D'font-family:微軟正黑體;font-size:11.0pt' lang=3Dzh-TW>突變導致的腎源性 SIADH</span><span
        style=3D'font-family:微軟正黑體;font-size:11.0pt' lang=3Den-US>(V2 receptor突變)</span><span
        style=3D'font-family:微軟正黑體;font-size:11.0pt' lang=3Dzh-TW>，使腎臟對 ADH 的反應增強。</span></li>
   </ul>
   <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;color:#366092'><span
       style=3D'font-family:微軟正黑體;font-size:14.0pt'>症狀</span></li>
   <ul type=3Dcircle style=3D'direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
    margin-bottom:0in'>
    <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
        style=3D'font-family:微軟正黑體;font-size:11.0pt'>低血鈉症</span></li>
    <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
        style=3D'font-family:微軟正黑體;font-size:11.0pt'>頭痛</span></li>
    <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
        style=3D'font-family:微軟正黑體;font-size:11.0pt'>噁心想吐</span></li>
    <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
